text.paragraph:
No information on the pharmacokinetics of Eulexin™ in hepatic impairment is available (see 
                                          BOXED WARNINGS, Hepatic Injury
                                       ).

Interactions between Eulexin™ capsules and LHRH-agonists have not occurred. Increases in prothrombin time have been noted in patients receiving warfarin therapy (see 
                                          PRECAUTIONS
                                       ).

Eulexin™ may cause fetal harm when administered to a pregnant woman (see 
                              Pregnancy
                           ).
